    "Firstly, intrinsic biases may exist within GPT-3's language model due to its training on vast internet text corpuses 37.",
    "As a result, it could be predisposed to generate a long explanation for complex social issues such as BLM movement.",
    "Secondly, and more importantly, extrinsic biases can be introduced by the users themselves 38.",
